    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-06-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-06-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="296" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d296">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Tindall</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr. Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Aylmer, Canada
                                    West,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-06-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">June</hi> 20, 1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir:</hi> I am directed to transmit to you the
                            enclosed resolution,<note n="*" xml:id="d296fn1">See Appendix, separate
                                volume.</note> which was unanimously passed at the late session of
                            the conference of the Methodist New Connexion church of Canada;</p>
                <p>And remain, yours, with respect,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>WILLIAM TINDALL,<hi rend="italic">Secretary of
                                Conference.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, U. S.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
